    CGI Holdings Inc.  
 Since 1982, CGI Holdings Inc. has grown from a small equipment rental company to a multifaceted construction services organization, employing almost 250 full-time workers during peak season.
CGIH continues to develop your construction business with;
-        Crane and equipment rentals
-        Heavy equipment and automotive repair
-        Construction management and services
-        Real estate
Today, owner Dan King and his team have diversified the business into eight strategic, interdisciplinary divisions, known collectively as CGI Holdings. Whether your project needs heavy equipment, knowledge of Labrador and joint partnerships, or camp management services, CGI and its subsidiaries are available to help build your business with a commitment to safety and environmental protection.
 





