    Capital Crane – Profile  
 Capital Crane provides all equipment needed for any large-scale construction site. We maintain a large, modern fleet, preventing your project from incurring additional costs associated with purchasing equipment, storage, or maintenance. From all-terrain cranes, to pickup trucks, Capital Crane has the turn-key equipment ready to meet the needs of any task.
The challenges of working in the cold and rough terrain of our province become no match for our fully winterized fleet.
Our safety, maintenance, and professional service departments use e-record keeping software tools which keep us up to date on maintenance planning, repair, and inspection activities. This ensures that the equipment you need is always readily available.





