Capital Springs - Profile | CGI Holdings Inc
















































 







    Capital Springs – Profile  
 Capital Springs was formed as a “leaf spring” company which has since evolved to offer other services, such as heavy equipment and trailer inspections. Our superior staff are trained in all aspects of government safety inspections to repair and rebuild your existing equipment. Our modern facility is equipped to accommodate large equipment and machinery. We ensure that every piece of construction equipment we service is in the best possible working order when it leaves our garage.
We manufacture and install springs for most makes and models of light and heavy duty trucks and trailers, led by an experienced technician whose work has been shipped province-wide.
Capital Springs also offers 24 hour service and is ready to meet your needs on the go, 24 hours a day.





