ABOUT CGI:

CGI was established in 1992 and has consistently built a reputation
based on designing and manufacturing quality impact resistant products
that meet or exceed the stringent Miami-Dade County impact standards.
The Company has over 200 employees at its manufacturing plant in Miami,
Florida. Today the Company continues to lead as an innovator, in
product craftsmanship, strength and style and its brands are highly
